{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ef6c42dc-73b7-4671-be43-bdaf74985265","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported in MSTest v3**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's how to replace each setting from your `local.testsettings`:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | MSTest v3 equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30000) | `<MSTest><Timeouts><TestTimeout>` in `.runsettings` or `[Timeout(30000)]` per-test |\n| Assembly resolution | No longer needed — MSTest v3 uses the modern test host |\n| Code coverage collector | `<DataCollectors>` section in `.runsettings` |\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file to replace it:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_sn3LnvyTIK6uhtZQOVu0Au","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-074eb65d570d478c8dbfd010f5eae66a/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Timeouts>\n      <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n    </Timeouts>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-074eb65d570d478c8dbfd010f5eae66a/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"9fb3ab7e-630f-4ad2-9790-9e46795097d5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Test deployment/assembly resolution configuration\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The configuration needs to be migrated to a `.runsettings` file and/or MSTest attributes/properties.\n\nLet me provide guidance on how to migrate each of these settings.","outputTokens":591,"requestId":"EC1A:23D3D5:64A4E0F:6D228F5:6A034B84"},"id":"90d95bc5-1539-4084-96fe-37201f470db1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:47:26.646Z","parentId":"0e41fc6e-4e63-4b5c-b786-f67fcdd17a17"}
